          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I fix my running rain jacket with some duct tape. And get locked into my new pack. It’s so clever. The strap system works so well and there are thoughtful pockets. I’ve chosen to try pack it today because it’s going to take me about four attempts before I settle on the right configuration. ",
